org.xchain.framework.net

Interface UrlExistsStrategy

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileUrlExistsStrategy, JarUrlExistsStrategy, ResourceUrlExistsStrategy

    public interface UrlExistsStrategy
    Interface for strategies to check if a URL references something that exists. Each UrlExistsStrategy is tied to a protocol.
    Author:
    Christian Trimble, Devon Tackett
